fields.name: Vortex Black Covers
fields.description: A bespoke set of 3D printed Vortex Black covers from our Stylish range, manufactured just for you. Express yourself with the Vortex Covers, a brand new dynamic design for Hero Arm users. While we have tried to represent the colour and design of our covers as best we can, the final product you receive may have slight differences depending on your fitted arm.
